Angluni chhib shai te avel:
# ekh chhib sostar biyandine aver neve chhiba, vai
# ekh vakyaripnasko sistemo ando vaxt kana kerden pen le anglune manushikane chhiba savo nai ekh chachi chhib.

==Chhiba kerde andar aver puraneder chhiba==
Ekh angluni chhib si ekh chhib savyatar aven le chhiba ekhe [[chhibavipnaski familiya|chhibavipnaske familiyake]]. Varesave anglune chhiba janglyoven mishto, ama aver si palem kerde andar familiyake chhiba sar thoven pen godyate ke sas. Kadya si i [[Angluni Indo-Europikani chhib|Angluni Indo-Europikani]], i [[Angluni Bantu chhib|Angluni Bantu]]

==Ekh vakyaripnasko systemo mai cira pherdo sar ekh chachi chhib==
Ekh angluni chhib so nai lake:
*ekh zorali, pherdi sintaksa;
*kernavnenge (verbonge) vaxta, navnenge paruvimata, th.a.
*ekh zoralo lavustik (vokabularo).

